author: jeffp
msg: Bug in Castor. Castor generated code which would not compile. Had to remove
import statement. This is caused by iCal XML <class> tag. Castor generates
a ClassDescriptor.java, but also imports its system ClassDescriptor class.
Must hack on this. There are some other descrepancies with Castor. These
center on the value attribute in the iCal XML.
